	<h1 class="title">中国游客变多之后，美国博物馆们如何应对？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Jane L. Levere</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-20 15:52:32 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7601/medium/7601.jpg?1436691852" alt="" />			
	</div>
